      "rationale": "Bench test conditions (flow rate ±0.2 L/min, rotational speed ±10 RPM, fluid temperature 22 ± 0.5 °C) are documented and match CFD boundary conditions. However, the test conditions span only a single thermal state. The COU describes OR deployment across 18–28 °C; no multi-temperature test matrix was executed. Humidity was uncontrolled and unreported. EMI from surgical equipment was not simulated or characterised during bench testing."
