      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published rotating-machinery benchmarks. Power-law haemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) is the regulatory standard. Model form uncertainty acknowledged for high-shear transient regions. No assessment of model form sensitivity to temperature-altered blood rheology was performed."
    },
    {
