      "rationale": "Blood density (1056 kg/m³), dynamic viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s at 22 °C), and haematocrit (40 %) are documented. Inlet velocity profiles derived from Doppler measurements. Input uncertainty propagation performed via ±5 % perturbation study. Viscosity temperature dependence across 18–28 °C (approximately 8 % variation) was not included in the input uncertainty characterisation, representing a gap relative to the COU environmental envelope."
    },
